author: Kevin Goddard
title: Ludacris - Vitamin D Feat. Ty Dolla $ign
text: 0 MAKE IT STOP Listen to Ludacris' new single "Vitamin D" featuring Ty Dolla Sign. It safe to say new music Friday is definitely upon us as the likes of Kendrick Lamar, Logic , YG, Asher Roth , Kodak Black , & Freddie Gibbs have all dropped off new music, but that’s not all. Joining in on the fun is ATL veteran Ludacris , who decides to link up with Ty Dolla Sign for a new single called “Vitamin D.” Putting a flip on Sisqo 's 2000 smash hit "Thong Song," Luda aims this one at the ladies & delivers a raunchy new bedroom cut. Hit play and share your thoughts on it (below).
